2 or more (max. 5) Level 4 Warrior-Type monstersDuring each of your opponent's End Phases: Detach 1 Xyz Material from this card. This card gains the following effects based on the number of Xyz Materials attached to it.● 1 or more: This card cannot be destroyed by battle.● 2 or more: This card gains 1500 ATK and DEF.● 3 or more: This card is unaffected by other card effects.● 4 or more: Your opponent cannot Normal/Special Summon.● 5 or more: Once per turn: You can destroy all cards your opponent controls.
